WEBVTT

00:04:29.042 --> 00:04:30.295
but there's no wireless,

00:04:30.319 --> 00:04:31.851
and in punk squats,

00:04:31.875 --> 00:04:34.813
everyone on the floor
in one room with no toilets

00:04:34.837 --> 00:04:37.832
but with wireless,
clearly making it the better option.

00:04:38.654 --> 00:04:40.412
(Laughter)

00:04:40.999 --> 00:04:47.065
My crew once pulled our van
up to a really poor Miami neighborhood

00:04:47.089 --> 00:04:49.771
and we found out that our couchsurfing
host for the night

00:04:49.795 --> 00:04:52.358
was an 18-year-old girl,
still living at home,

00:04:52.382 --> 00:04:56.485
and her family were all undocumented
immigrants from Honduras.

00:04:57.006 --> 00:05:00.382
And that night, her whole family